item.dc:creator: @legendofjon legendofjon
item.description:
@legendofjon wrote:

It’s not because you have imac,
The “x” at the upper left is very common.
That happens to me couple of time, what i do to solve it.
For web client:
If your using internet explorer, try on mozzilla firefox, if your using it on internet explorer, switch to mozzilla. It usually works, the chance of both of them having a x at the upper left are very low.
